        "created_at": "2025-04-23T07:59:16.644Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This service will most useful to whistleblowers of corporations and govts who will be running Signal on a tails USB behind Tor. So you can assume they have enough computational power.</p>\n<p>Signal is already replacing SecureDrop as the service of choice for many media orgs to receive tips from whistleblowers. You can search the websites of various media/news orgs for how they receive tips.</p>\n<p>There are sufficiently high profile whistleblowers for whom Signal+tails is not good enough, namely whistleblowers of the US intelligence community leaking classified documents. For other whistleblowers though Signal+tails may be enough.</p>",
